        <Parent_String>ozokerite (ozokerite) [300014600], mineral wax [300014598], wax by composition or origin [300187974], wax [300014585], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
